Re: Help on Hiragana from youtube video...
by Hyperworm » Tue 07.14.2009 8:45 am Actually, I think it's そうはいかないわ.(lit: "as for that way, it won't go" = "It's not going to go that way" = "I don't think so! / No way! / etc")
