Re: Help on Hiragana from youtube video...
by Hyperworm » Thu 07.16.2009 11:52 am My post there was just an attempt to show the (or, at least, a possible) reason why the sentence means what it does.It wasn't a justification for いかない, which I'm quite sure is correct anyway through personal experience and google results. Sorry if I was a bit confusing Results 1 - 10 of about 1,800,000 for "そうはいかない". Results 1 - 10 of about 185 for "そうはいけない".
